{"tid":999512,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵根本要有權同有責任捉煙鏟","createTime":"2019-01-28T18:12:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-29T03:09:53.000Z","uid":135306,"like":30,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"26e6f9287e93df4a9c2c618045c33c0f12d4160e","tid":999512,"uid":135306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T18:12:55.000Z","msg":"宜家話就話唔比堆煙鏟係公眾地方食煙<br />\n但實際上根本都係成班煙鏟照係港鐵出面有蓋既地方食煙<br />\n<br />\n你打去1823/ 控煙辦 屌一次佢先做一兩次野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 根本係治標唔治本 而事實上 香港咁大 冇可能日日都擺一堆控煙辦既人係香港18區捉煙鏟<br />\n <br />\n咁問題就黎啦 你又可以同港鐵投訴 但佢只會做樣咁派條友去趕班煙鏟走 咁又有撚用咩屌你老母？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以我話 根本應該強逼港鐵處理好煙鏟既問題 因為港鐵本身個個站都有staff 只有佢地做多一步 有人投訴 就要帶埋手機影低佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 記低d資料 每日send 番比控煙辦去罰佢地錢 （認就罰 唔認就攞番條片出黎做證據罰三倍）咁先做到班煙鏟嫁嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申： 好憎煙鏟 煙鏟死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04e78d668509f154fe596bda14c1681fdc4379a9","tid":999512,"uid":135306,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T18:18:13.000Z","msg":"負皮講下原因？"},{"pid":"1ff21a93d00b615dd40911e76979366d30cd4dbd","tid":999512,"uid":193110,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"04e78d668509f154fe596bda14c1681fdc4379a9","tid":999512,"uid":135306,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T18:18:13.000Z","msg":"負皮講下原因？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T18:33:42.000Z","msg":"皮已正<br />\n煙剷負皮嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a04f56f0b89938abe16f12141278d2f743865c93","tid":999512,"uid":104225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T18:48:37.000Z","msg":"行出一步咪繼續食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到時又話食環有責任云云"},{"pid":"862858c19eaf89ef6349837c10529bbf84ea010a","tid":999512,"uid":182707,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T18:59:51.000Z","msg":"其實唔係有蓋就一定唔食得煙，例如大部分行人天橋都可以食煙的，留意下啲垃圾桶有冇得掉丫煙頭就會知道。"},{"pid":"b838a3990bf7884717eac9bf32055263054ceec1","tid":999512,"uid":135306,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"a04f56f0b89938abe16f12141278d2f743865c93","tid":999512,"uid":104225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T18:48:37.000Z","msg":"行出一步咪繼續食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到時又話食環有責任云云"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T23:45:03.000Z","msg":"行出左一步之後根本都冇犯法<br />\n雖然都係食煙 但暫都係吹佢地唔漲 食環冇責任啊 <br />\n但唔係冇用 至少都可以慢慢逼到煙鏟真係愈黎愈少地方食<br />\n<br />\n我講緊個重點係 宜家話就話就大部分室內地方/ 港鐵外出地方禁煙 你寫都唔比 但煙鏟照係你「禁上吸煙」個牌下面照食係咩原因？ 係因為冇人/ 唔夠人 執法<br />\n<br />\n所以我講緊係理論上唔應該只係港鐵有權有責任 而係所有商場/ 地頭蟲 都應該要管到煙鏟食煙個問題 而有舉報唔做野 應該佢地都要罰埋"},{"pid":"d7b4d50e1be337718ae77faa8ddf4329452bcc81","tid":999512,"uid":29914,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T01:35:10.000Z","msg":"啫係俾港鐵有埋執法權？"},{"pid":"5bd24f16abea9ae822d32b5f2f52861f397b51d3","tid":999512,"uid":233175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T01:36:47.000Z","msg":"煙鏟正仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n皮已正"},{"pid":"11a4c797e4f4712c0f8eb51ff5ad363409fedb97","tid":999512,"uid":70301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T01:49:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>行出一步咪繼續食<br />\n到時又話食環有責任云云</blockquote><br />\n控煙辦係衛生署㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed1d543a73ef6038eaf704defde0cb458b2417fb","tid":999512,"uid":115525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T01:54:30.000Z","msg":"我直頭覺得 控煙辦要好似請aco咁請一堆人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌啦星 大把垃圾桶上面無裝煙灰個位 d仆街都照辣落去d垃圾桶度<br />\nd橙色垃圾桶 好似劉江華咁 地中海 中間白色既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba7ca372e71b6b873d7404a37ed9c37d37603e0b","tid":999512,"uid":135306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7b4d50e1be337718ae77faa8ddf4329452bcc81","tid":999512,"uid":29914,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T01:35:10.000Z","msg":"啫係俾港鐵有埋執法權？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T02:51:37.000Z","msg":"我諗比港鐵執法係有爭議既<br />\n<br />\n但係至少應該施加d責任比佢 <br />\n要佢 （同埋所有公眾場所負責人）：<br />\n1） 接到市民投訴要影低煙鏟<br />\n2） 定期將資料提交比控煙辦做野<br />\n<br />\n就好似你商場/ 租個單位比人 你都有責任確保佢唔係做緊犯法野啦 （例如吸/藏毒）"},{"pid":"80f7e9e7152d7faf36139b7484e02c990dbefdf7","tid":999512,"uid":29914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba7ca372e71b6b873d7404a37ed9c37d37603e0b","tid":999512,"uid":135306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7b4d50e1be337718ae77faa8ddf4329452bcc81","tid":999512,"uid":29914,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T01:35:10.000Z","msg":"啫係俾港鐵有埋執法權？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T02:51:37.000Z","msg":"我諗比港鐵執法係有爭議既<br />\n<br />\n但係至少應該施加d責任比佢 <br />\n要佢 （同埋所有公眾場所負責人）：<br />\n1） 接到市民投訴要影低煙鏟<br />\n2） 定期將資料提交比控煙辦做野<br />\n<br />\n就好似你商場/ 租個單位比人 你都有責任確保佢唔係做緊犯法野啦 （例如吸/藏毒）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T03:09:53.000Z","msg":"或者參考警方做法，派駐一至兩名控煙辦職員係港鐵站，幫助執法。"}]}